      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RIVERSIDE BEAST (6) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (20.21) in a Grade 6 at Murray Bridge. Better than last start and worth following up. YARRAMUNDI CAMMO (4) ran a nice race two back to fill a minor placing then got off the mark last time (17.67) at Murray Bridge over 300m. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. ZING MATILDA (2) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only 0.8 lengths from the winner Zipping Beluga in third(17.54) at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings six times from seven starts. Expected to feature. VAPOUR GLOW (1) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
